Noah Gift 👋

What currently keeps me busy is working as an Executive in Residence at the Duke MIDS (Data Science) and Duke AI Product Management program and as a consultant and author in Cloud Computing, Big Data, DevOps, and MLOps. The following visual resume is a good idea to show the kinds of things I have worked on in my life. I am a Rust Fanatic.

What You Will Learn
